Ask him if he's going to do what I offered.

114
00:09:22,137 --> 00:09:26,119
If he agrees to do it, I'll order him to get rid of them both tonight.

115
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,939
Kill Tanya.

116
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,450
Your second choice.

117
00:09:38,975 --> 00:09:41,659
Kill Nuengdiao.

118
