127
00:12:58,302 --> 00:13:00,299
How did you know that?

128
00:13:00,299 --> 00:13:02,140
I'll tell you later.

129
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,990
It's not safe here.

130
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:06,107
