144
00:14:20,005 --> 00:14:22,036
That's right.

145
00:14:22,036 --> 00:14:23,682
I'm an asshole.

146
00:14:23,682 --> 00:14:25,699
I'm selfish.

147
00:14:26,347 --> 00:14:28,147
Palm.

148
00:14:28,147 --> 00:14:29,797
What's wrong?

149
00:14:29,797 --> 00:14:32,557
You don't need to do everything on your own.

150
00:14:32,557 --> 00:14:34,329
If something is bothering you, you can tell me.

151
00:14:34,329 --> 00:14:37,062
All you need to do is talk to me.

152
00:14:38,785 --> 00:14:40,760
It's Supakit.

153
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:45,159
He told me to kill either Mrs. Tanya or you in exchange for my dad's life.

154
00:14:49,331 --> 00:14:51,505
Did you kill my mom?

155
00:14:51,505 --> 00:14:55,392
No, I didn't. I didn't do anything to her.

156
