160
00:15:30,686 --> 00:15:32,249
I'm sorry.

161
00:15:32,249 --> 00:15:34,194
But my dad's life is on the line.

162
00:15:34,194 --> 00:15:35,945
I didn't know what to do.

163
00:15:35,945 --> 00:15:37,653
I'm sorry.

164
00:15:38,399 --> 00:15:40,202
Then kill me.

165
00:15:40,202 --> 00:15:43,438
Kill me, Palm. If you kill me, everything will be over.

166
