Do it. Kill me.

170
00:15:49,587 --> 00:15:51,284
Kill me.

171
00:15:51,284 --> 00:15:54,040
Do it, Palm. Kill me. Shoot me.

172
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,671
If you kill me, everything will be over.

173
